{
  "name": "Example: Simple VLA",
  "description": "Demo-level VLA rollout: Octo-Small on SimplerEnv as a single predict node inside the standard observe -> predict -> step loop. Built-in loop skeleton (iterIn / iterOut / termination) + the simpler env nodeset's gym verbs + one policy node. Lean variant of vla/unverified/octo_simpler.json kept as a minimal teaching example.",
  "step_budget": 80,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "env_reset",
      "type": "env_simpler__reset",
      "label": "SIMPLER: Reset",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "seed_obs",
      "type": "env_simpler__observe_egocentric",
      "label": "SIMPLER: Observe (seed)",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 200
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "iter_in",
      "type": "iterIn",
      "label": "Iteration Gate",
      "position": {
        "x": 280,
        "y": 0
      },
      "config": {
        "pairedWith": "iter_out",
        "initPorts": [
          {
            "name": "instruction",
            "wire_type": "TEXT",
            "persist": true,
            "required": true
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "predict",
      "type": "policy_octo__predict",
      "label": "Octo: Predict",
      "position": {
        "x": 560,
        "y": 0
      },
      "config": {
        "checkpoint_path": "",
        "model_type": "octo-small",
        "policy_setup": "widowx_bridge",
        "horizon": 2,
        "pred_action_horizon": 4,
        "exec_horizon": 1,
        "image_size": 256,
        "action_scale": 1.0,
        "init_rng": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "env_step",
      "type": "env_simpler__step_continuous",
      "label": "SIMPLER: Step",
      "position": {
        "x": 840,
        "y": 0
      },
      "config": {
        "max_chunk_steps": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "loop_obs",
      "type": "env_simpler__observe_egocentric",
      "label": "SIMPLER: Observe (loop)",
      "position": {
        "x": 1120,
        "y": 200
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "iter_out",
      "type": "iterOut",
      "label": "Iteration End",
      "position": {
        "x": 1400,
        "y": 0
      },
      "config": {
        "pairedWith": "iter_in",
        "ports": [
          {
            "name": "agentview_image",
            "wire_type": "IMAGE",
            "persist": true,
            "required": true
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "evaluate",
      "type": "env_simpler__evaluate",
      "label": "SIMPLER: Evaluate",
      "position": {
        "x": 1400,
        "y": 360
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "output_port__success",
      "type": "graphOut",
      "label": "success",
      "position": {
        "x": 1680,
        "y": 320
      },
      "config": {
        "portName": "success",
        "wireType": "BOOL"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "output_port__metrics",
      "type": "graphOut",
      "label": "metrics",
      "position": {
        "x": 1680,
        "y": 420
      },
      "config": {
        "portName": "metrics",
        "wireType": "METRICS"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "note_demo",
      "type": "note",
      "label": "Demo: built-in VLA loop",
      "position": {
        "x": 560,
        "y": -280
      },
      "config": {
        "markdown": "**Demo: a VLA rollout from built-in parts only**\n\nThe whole agent is the built-in loop skeleton (`iterIn` / `iterOut` / `termination`) around the simpler nodeset's gym verbs (reset / observe / step / evaluate) plus **one** policy node (`policy_octo__predict`). No glue code.\n\n- `policy_setup` must match the SIMPLER split chosen in the env panel (`widowx_bridge` vs `google_robot`).\n- Empty `checkpoint_path` falls back to `data/vla_policy/checkpoints/octo-small-1.5`, then `hf://rail-berkeley/octo-small`.\n\nFull-featured variant with operational notes: `vla/unverified/octo_simpler.json`."
      }
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    {
      "id": "e_reset_instruction_to_init",
      "source": "env_reset",
      "target": "iter_in",
      "sourceHandle": "instruction",
      "targetHandle": "init_instruction"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_reset_to_seedobs",
      "source": "env_reset",
      "target": "seed_obs",
      "sourceHandle": "episode_id",
      "targetHandle": "trigger"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_seedobs_to_iterin",
      "source": "seed_obs",
      "target": "iter_in",
      "sourceHandle": "agentview_image",
      "targetHandle": "iterout_agentview_image"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_iterin_instruction_to_predict",
      "source": "iter_in",
      "target": "predict",
      "sourceHandle": "init_instruction",
      "targetHandle": "instruction"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_iterin_image_to_predict",
      "source": "iter_in",
      "target": "predict",
      "sourceHandle": "iterout_agentview_image",
      "targetHandle": "image"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_predict_to_step",
      "source": "predict",
      "target": "env_step",
      "sourceHandle": "action_chunk",
      "targetHandle": "action"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_step_info_to_loopobs",
      "source": "env_step",
      "target": "loop_obs",
      "sourceHandle": "info",
      "targetHandle": "trigger"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_loopobs_to_iterout",
      "source": "loop_obs",
      "target": "iter_out",
      "sourceHandle": "agentview_image",
      "targetHandle": "agentview_image"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_step_terminated_to_termination__stop",
      "source": "env_step",
      "target": "iter_out",
      "sourceHandle": "terminated",
      "targetHandle": "stop"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_evaluate_success_to_graphout",
      "source": "evaluate",
      "target": "output_port__success",
      "sourceHandle": "success",
      "targetHandle": "value"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_evaluate_metrics_to_graphout",
      "source": "evaluate",
      "target": "output_port__metrics",
      "sourceHandle": "metrics",
      "targetHandle": "value"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_iter_out_finalstop_to_evaluate",
      "source": "iter_out",
      "sourceHandle": "final_stop",
      "target": "evaluate",
      "targetHandle": "trigger"
    }
  ]
}
